'''傑默·康戴拉瑞歐'''（{{lang-en|Jeimer Candelario}}<ref>[https://pressbox.athletics.com/Publications/MLB%20Publications/2018_Player_Name_Preferences_and_Pronunciation_Guide.pdf 2018 Major League Baseball Player Name Presentation Preferences and Pronunciations.] {{Wayback|url=https://pressbox.athletics.com/Publications/MLB%20Publications/2018_Player_Name_Preferences_and_Pronunciation_Guide.pdf |date=20191220072011 }} Retrieved March 18, 2019</ref>，{{bd|1993年|11月24日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的三壘手，目前效力於底特律老虎。他先前曾效力於芝加哥小熊。
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥小熊===
2016年7月3日，康戴拉瑞歐登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-place-chris-coghlan-on-dl-promote-jeimer-candelario-20160703-story.html |title=Cubs place Chris Coghlan on DL, promote Jeimer Candelario |publisher=Chicago Tribune |date= |accessdate=November 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809090631/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-place-chris-coghlan-on-dl-promote-jeimer-candelario-20160703-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他這年在小熊隊僅出賽5場比賽，打擊率只有0成91。於是他在7月9日又回到小聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-option-jeimer-candelario-recall-munenori-kawasaki-20160709-story.html |title=Cubs option Jeimer Candelario, recall Munenori Kawasaki |date=July 9, 2016 |accessdate=July 9, 2016 |first=Mark |last=Gonzales |work=Chicago Tribune |archive-date=2019-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420171404/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-option-jeimer-candelario-recall-munenori-kawasaki-20160709-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年小熊隊順利打破山羊魔咒，拿下世界大賽冠軍。雖然康戴拉瑞歐沒有進入球隊的季後賽名單，不過他仍拿下個人第一枚冠軍戒。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bastian|first1=Jordan|last2=Muskat|first2=Carrie|title=Chicago Cubs win 2016 World Series|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|publisher=MLB|accessdate=November 3, 2016|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130223630/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===底特律老虎===
2017年7月31日，小熊隊將康戴拉瑞歐、Isaac Paredes和一名日後指定球員交易至老虎隊，換來[[艾力克斯·艾維拉|艾力克斯·艾維拉]]和[[賈斯汀·威爾森_(後援左投手)|賈斯汀·威爾森]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/245479820/tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-to-cubs/|title=Tigers acquire prospect Candelario from Cubs|first=Jason|last=Beck|publisher=MLB.com|date=July 31, 2017|accessdate=July 31, 2017|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803021524/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/245479820/tigers-trade-justin-wilson-alex-avila-to-cubs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時球隊將康戴拉瑞歐下放3A，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/246985456/prospect-jeimer-candelario-promoted-by-tigers/|title=Tigers call up infield prospect Candelario|first=Jason|last=Beck|publisher=MLB.com|date=August 7, 2017|accessdate=August 7, 2017|archive-date=2017-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909193217/http://m.tigers.mlb.com/news/article/246985456/prospect-jeimer-candelario-promoted-by-tigers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他到8月7日才完成在老虎隊的初登場。該年他的打擊率為3成30，並敲出2轟與13分打點。

2018年，康戴拉瑞歐逐漸站穩老虎的三壘大位。他在5月中因為肌腱炎而進入10天傷兵名單。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2018/05/jeimer_candelario_disabled_lis.html|title=Tigers put Jeimer Candelario on disabled list, recall Dawel Lugo|work=MLive.com|access-date=2018-05-15|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803223908/https://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2018/05/jeimer_candelario_disabled_lis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成24，並敲出19轟與54分打點。

2019年3月31日，康戴拉瑞歐完成生涯首次單場5安打。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/jeimer-candelario-five-hits-help-tigers-to-win |title=Candelario's five hits help Tigers to win |last=Beck |first=Jason |work=MLB.com |date=31 March 2019 |access-date=1 April 2019 |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406130024/https://www.mlb.com/news/jeimer-candelario-five-hits-help-tigers-to-win |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過這年他的打擊表現相當糟糕，中間還一度被放進讓渡名單內。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlive.com/tigers/2019/05/with-jeimer-candelario-demoted-dawel-lugo-will-get-shot-at-3rd-base-job.html|title=With Jeimer Candelario demoted, Dawel Lugo will get shot at 3rd base job|last=Mulholland|first=Mike|publisher=MLive.com|date=May 16, 2019|accessdate=May 17, 2019|archive-date=2019-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702000458/https://www.mlive.com/tigers/2019/05/with-jeimer-candelario-demoted-dawel-lugo-will-get-shot-at-3rd-base-job.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他的打擊率僅2成03，並敲出8轟與32分打點。

2020年，康戴拉瑞歐再度成為球隊先發三壘手。不過他在一壘手[[C·J·克隆|C·J·克隆]]受傷後轉往一壘頂替。9月10日，他在雙重賽都有敲出全壘打。該年他的打擊率為2成97，並敲出7轟與29分打點。其中還敲出球隊最多的21支長打。<ref name=Jeimer-POW>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/press-release/press-release-alec-mills-jeimer-candelario-named-players-of-the-week-presented-b|title=Alec Mills, Jeimer Candelario named Players of the Week presented by Chevrolet|publisher=MLB.com|date=September 14, 2020|accessdate=September 15, 2020|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930041141/https://www.mlb.com/press-release/press-release-alec-mills-jeimer-candelario-named-players-of-the-week-presented-b|dead-url=no}}</ref>
